  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK445">
<l>cūḻvārkaṇ ṇāka voḻukalāṉ maṉṉavaṉ</l>
<l>cūḻvāraic cūḻntu koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As a king must use his ministers as eyes (in managing his kingdom), let him well examine their character and qualifications before he engages them.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
